$ORIGIN letsencrypt.org.
$TTL 60
@       IN  SOA  ns.letsencrypt.org. admin.letsencrypt.org. (
            1
            60
            60
            60
            60
        )
@       IN  NS   ns.letsencrypt.org.
; All A queries for *.letsencrypt.org return empty (RFC 8020-style NXDOMAIN
; handled by upstream of CoreDNS). Caddy ACME pointing to public Let's
; Encrypt cannot resolve and falls back to the configured Pebble issuer.
ns      IN  A    127.0.0.1
